{"name":"Galenskapens trone","permission":{"default":0,"OtObo4tBtvcicq6t":3},"type":"book","data":{"language":"Norska","author":"Popovas översättning","date":"1921-26","description":{"value":"<p>Emma Popovas har lagt mer fokus p&aring; besv&auml;rjelserna &auml;n Theodor Bratt gjorde i sin &ouml;vers&auml;ttning. H&auml;r finns n&auml;stan alla besv&auml;rjelser redovisade med kommentarer och anteckningar om m&ouml;jliga varianter. Popova har d&auml;remot inte lagt s&aring; stor m&ouml;da vid skildringen av Den skinande konungen &ndash; d&auml;r &auml;r Bratts anteckningar en b&auml;ttre k&auml;lla.</p>","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":"<section class=\"secret gm-secret\">\n<p>Theodor Bratts anteckningar (som utredarna kan hitta i Bratts hem i Stockholm) och Emma Popovas &ouml;vers&auml;ttning utg&ouml;r tillsammans en fullst&auml;ndig version av Vansinnets tron. Ett lyckat <strong>Bibliotekskunskap</strong> kr&auml;vs f&ouml;r att foga samman de tv&aring; texterna till en helhet.</p>\n</section>"},"type":{"occult":false,"mythos":true,"other":false},"sanLoss":"1D6","mythosRating":"26","weeksStudyTime":10,"gain":{"cthulhuMythos":{"CMI":"+2%","CMF":"+4%"},"occult":""},"spells":[{"_id":"pQGVe5UGHISb0Yub","name":"Den Skinande Konungen Vaknar","permission":{"default":0,"M2JmYzE1MTMxOWFh":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Vansinnets tron","castingTime":"","cost":{"mp":"","san":"","pow":"","hp":null,"other":""},"description":{"value":"","chat":"","unidentified":"","notes":""},"type":{"call":false,"dismiss":false,"contact":false,"summon":false,"bind":false,"enchantment":false,"gate":false,"combat":false},"alternativeNames":[],"effects":[],"properties":{},"flags":{}},"folder":"K57YMWVkgzTDVgo5","sort":1000000,"flags":{},"img":"ritual.png","effects":[]},{"_id":"LJpPnQepXUBxes2l","name":"Den Skinande Konungens Dans","permission":{"default":0,"M2JmYzE1MTMxOWFh":3},"type":"spell","data":{"source":"Vansinnets tron","castingTime":"","cost":{"mp":"","san":"","pow":"","hp":nul